OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,FJack Draper has warned tennis must
OL,7,Faddress its growing injury crisis.
OL,9,FThe 24-year-old from Sutton will play
OL,10,Fjust his 15th match since Wimbledon
OL,11,Flast year when he takes on sixth seed
OL,12,FTaylor Fritz in the opening round at
OL,13,Fthe All England Club on Tuesday.
OL,15,FDraper was absent for the best part of
OL,16,Fseven months following his second-
OL,17,Fround exit 12 months ago because of
OL,18,Fbone bruising in his arm, while he was
OL,19,Fthen forced to take another break due
OL,20,Fto knee and shoulder issues.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
