PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,FThe former US Open semi-finalist has
OL,7,Fat least recovered in time for his
OL,8,Fhome grand slam but there have already
OL,9,Fbeen 10 withdrawals on the men's side,
OL,10,Fincluding two-time former champion
OL,11,FCarlos Alcaraz, who is taking his
OL,12,Ffirst steps back on court as he
OL,13,Frecovers from a wrist injury.
OL,15,FThe gruelling nature of the tour, the
OL,16,Fincreasingly physical style of play as
OL,17,Fwell as the speed of courts and balls
OL,18,Fhave all been cited as reasons for the
OL,19,Fgrowing list of absentees at big
OL,20,Ftournaments.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,FDraper said: "I was really trying to
OL,7,Fdevelop my game and push my game more
OL,8,Fand more every week to reach those
OL,9,Fguys like Alcaraz and (Jannik) Sinner,
OL,10,Fwho obviously play at an incredibly
OL,11,Fhigh level. I just broke down.
OL,13,F"I think it's pretty worrying the
OL,14,Fstate of men's tennis, especially
OL,15,Fright now. The amount of injuries,
OL,16,Fespecially young players.
OL,26,@nD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,F"When I look at the draws for the
OL,7,Fweeks when I was out, everything is
OL,8,Fshoulder, arm, wrist. I think
OL,9,Fdefinitely the way athletes are
OL,10,Fgetting better and hitting the ball
OL,11,Fharder and moving better, I think it's
OL,12,Fmy opinion they need to really take a
OL,13,Fclose look at what we're doing on tour.
OL,15,F"Definitely the state of the Masters
OL,16,F1000s, the 12-day events. I was privy
OL,17,Fto those conversations when I was a
OL,18,Ftop-10 player. Now I'm not. I don't
OL,19,Fcare as much about what I say. I think
OL,20,Fthe tournaments are going to suffer a
OL,21,Flot if not much changes."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
