OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt has been a hugely challenging
OL,12,Fperiod for Draper, who has slipped all
OL,13,Fthe way down to 160 in the rankings.
OL,15,F"It's very difficult," he said. "When
OL,16,FI was younger, I had quite a few
OL,17,Fsetbacks. Then I came through that and
OL,18,Fhad a couple years of where I wasn't.
OL,19,FI made some incredible progress.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@VO]wD@aOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,F"Looking back, coming here last year
OL,7,Fas four in the world, I was feeling
OL,8,Fincredible and looking forward to
OL,9,Feverything that was to come. I felt
OL,10,Flike I was gradually building up and
OL,11,Fup and up, confidence in my tennis, in
OL,12,Fmy body, in my mind.
OL,14,F"Then you have something that stops
OL,15,Fyou in your tracks when you're not
OL,16,Fexpecting it. It's really difficult to
OL,17,Faccept that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,F"I think my tennis hasn't gone
OL,7,Fanywhere because I've really been
OL,8,Fdedicated every day to try and do
OL,9,Feverything possible so that, when I am
OL,10,Fback on court, like now, I'm in a good
OL,11,Fplace.
OL,13,F"I still believe, even now after all
OL,14,Fthis time, I'm still competing at an
OL,15,Fincredibly high level. I'm looking
OL,16,Fforward to working my way up again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
