PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,FDraper will go into Tuesday's match on
OL,7,FCentre Court buoyed by a run to the
OL,8,Fsemi-finals in Eastbourne this week in
OL,9,Fhis comeback event and first with new
OL,10,Fcoach Andy Murray by his side.
OL,12,FHe would have hoped for a
OL,13,Fsignificantly easier first opponent
OL,14,Fthan Fritz, but it is an unlucky draw
OL,15,Ffor both men.
OL,17,FThe American is trying to see the
OL,18,Fpositives of it, saying: "It's a good
OL,19,Fopportunity to have a really exciting
OL,20,Ffirst round that everyone's going to
OL,21,Fbe paying attention to.
OL,26,@zD@ZOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1782728295
OL,3,CJack Draper reveals worry about state
OL,4,Cof men's tennis as injuries pile up
OL,6,F"I think, for both of us, it's not the
OL,7,Fthing you love to see, but I've had a
OL,8,Flot of success when I've had tough
OL,9,Fdraws in tournaments.
OL,11,F"If I lose in the first round or I
OL,12,Flose in the fourth round, to be
OL,13,Fhonest, it's all the same to me. I'm
OL,14,Ftrying to go deeper than that.
OL,16,F"He's going to come out super hungry
OL,17,Fand there's not really any pressure on
OL,18,Fhim, so I think that makes it
OL,19,Fdangerous."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
